                            <a href="http://docs.jelix.org/en/manual-1.4/create-wizard">the wizard</a> of jelix,
                            and your application is installed and ready to use in few clicks</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section">
                        <h2>Choose Jelix!</h2>
